value.0: Once a well-fed halfling, now a mummified corpse. A trail of trinkets around him suggests he had a lousy sense of timing and a limited amount of food. He holds a cheap copper ring in his shriveled right hand.
These tracks look to have been left by a humanoid creature.
A black barrel - made of stone and reinforced with metal bands - a simple and cheap storage solution.

This bloodsmeared sign holds a clear and visible skull, with two crossed bones behind it. Even though the message, which was formerly written at the bottom, is no longer visible, the graphic appearance of the sign sends a clear indication that travelling any further would be very dangerous.
The chain disappears into some unseen recess above you where it presumably activates some hidden mechanism.
